page.title: 20LIFE STYLE HOBBIES INTERESTS
page.content: Activities reported by one person only included aikido, archery, ballet, bee keeping, boating, car repairing, cake decorating, cards, chess, church, cinema visiting, doll making, dining out, drama, dominoes, training gun dogs, gymnastics, health club visiting, hiking, jigsaws, local history, mountaineering, motor cycling, pottery, pot holing, amature radio, record collecting, skittles, stamp collecting, trampolining, upholstery, weight training, wind surfing, wine making, wrestling and youth work. This survey was conducted on one day only and thus the above list may not be fully comprehensive.
